OL,5, An unexpected call turned out to be the
OL,6, sweetest thing for a bookshop after it 
OL,7, hosted a visit from a music superstar. 
OL,9,FJo Legerton, who works at Manchester's 
OL,10,FChorlton Bookshop, said she thought it 
OL,11,Fwas "a hoax" when someone rang to say  
OL,12,FBono would be visiting on Saturday.    
OL,14,FHowever, it ended up being a beautiful 
OL,15,Fday as the U2 singer popped in for 45  
OL,16,Fminutes, ahead of his show in the city.
OL,18,FMs Legerton said she jokingly asked if 
OL,19,Fhe had a desire to do Christmas shifts 
OL,20,Fat the shop, but he sadly declined.    
